Shaw Brick-Dartmouth
Shaw Brick is an Atlantic Canadian based manufacturer of quality clay masonry and concrete landscape products. Building on a tradition established in 1861, Shaw Brick continues to blend traditional values and innovative solutions to offer a variety of brick collections and stone products that will add an exclusive dimension to the design of your home.  Shaw Brick’s durable landscape products add elegance and appeal to any outdoor living space. The versatility and array of shapes, colours, and patterns available in driveway & walkway pavers, garden walls, landscape walls and retaining wall systems offer you unlimited design possibilities. 








