Company - Calysta - Innovative and Sustainable Industrial Products














































 



 







CompanyYou are here: Home / Company






Company
Creating Value Through Innovation
Calysta is an innovator in sustainable products to improve worldwide food security. Calysta is developing and commercializing FeedKind® protein, a sustainable, traceable alternative feed ingredient for fish, livestock and pet nutritional products.

 



